<h1>Welcome ADMINISTRATOR!</h1>
<h4>You can do whatever you wish...</h4>

<p><em>Fear is the mind-killer.
Fear is the little-death that brings total obliteration.
I will face my fear.
I will permit it to pass over me and through me.
And when it has gone past I will turn the inner eye to see its path.
Where the fear has gone there will be nothing.
Only I will remain.</em></p>

<% if current_administrator %>
  <p>
    <%= current_administrator.name %> ... is logged in
  </p>
  <%= link_to "Log-Out", log_out_path, method: :delete %>
  <%= render "logged_in" %>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to "Log-In", log_in_path %><br />
  <%= link_to "Log-In as MAESTRO", '/maestros' %><br />
  <%= link_to "Browse Schools", schools_path %><br />
<% end %>



<h1>List of all 'Administrators'</h1>

<ul>
  <% @administrators.each do |administrator| %>
    <li>
      <%= administrator.email %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
